<h3>Broader replication, Nature publication</h3>
<p style="font-size:14px;">50+ published studies across multiple independent research groups. Stronger independent verification than BPC-157. Cardiac regeneration data published in Nature. Muscle satellite cell activation well-documented. Limitation: less total volume, no human trials for musculoskeletal applications.</p>
</div>
</div>

